original_title: อนึ่ง คิดถึงพอสังเขป รุ่น 2
overview: Three months after new semester starts, but this boy marching band, the band that owned a world champion, still cannot find new members. More than half of the band graduated last semester and new generation of students like to play guitar, keyboard and drum rather than music instruments in the marching band.
title: I Miss You 2
